        			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        				<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
        					                                <p>He pono n&#333; kou i mea unuhi &#8216;&#333;lelo nou me ke k&#257;ki &#8216;ole, koe no n&#257; polokalamu a i &#8216;ole n&#257; kumu e pono ai ka m&#257;kaukau ma ka &#8216;&#333;lelo Pelek&#257;nia no ke komo &#8216;ana i ka hana. <a href="https://forms.gle/LkWFEhqoY8Ly5ySHA" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Palapala noi maanei.</a></p>
                    					<button type="button" class="rounded-md bg-white text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2 closeLanguageBar">
